<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.1">
<l>tāvaḷan tulaka muṟṟun taṭamalarp poykai pukku</l>
<l>nāvaḷam naviṉṟaṅ kētta nākattiṉ  naṭukkan tīrttāy</l>
<l>māvaḷam peruki maṉṉum maṟaiyavar vāḻum nāṅkaik</l>
<l>kāvaḷam pāṭi mēya kaṇṇaṉē kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, having [once] measured the whole world in a leap,</l>
<l>Allayed the fear of the elephant which, entering a wide blossoming pond, praised</l>
<l rend="indent">[you] there, uttering the bounty of the tongue,</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ who dwells in the hamlet of Kāvaḷam in Nāṅkai where live</l>
<l>Experts in the Vedas, which endure increasing great bounty,</l>
<l rend="indent">only you are [our] refuge!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
